entry.title: In Dueling Remarks, Biden and Netanyahu Spar Over Gaza's Future
entry.content: President Biden and Israel’s prime minister clashed over who should govern Gaza after the war, in a remarkable public display of differences emerging between the two leaders.

entry.title: Israel Begins Pumping Seawater Into Hamas's Gaza Tunnels
entry.content: The effort, which is at an early stage, is part of an intensive campaign to destroy the underground infrastructure that has underpinned the militant group’s operations.
